OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FParcel firms told to       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fimprove how they handle    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcomplaints                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parcel firms will be expected to       
OL,6, improve how they handle complaints     
OL,7, under new proposals aimed at improving 
OL,8, customer service.                      
OL,10,FRegulator Ofcom said nearly two-thirds 
OL,11,Fof customers it surveyed in January had
OL,12,Fsuffered problems with deliveries.     
OL,14,FWhen things go wrong, such as parcels  
OL,15,Fbeing lost, customers often have       
OL,16,Fproblems resolving complaints, it said.
OL,18,FDeliveries have grown significantly in 
OL,19,Fthe pandemic driven by rapid growth in 
OL,20,Fonline shopping.                       
